        <div class="body">
            <p>Matthew, you have explained it fully so there is no sense to say the same in another words, I guess :)</p>

<p>If you wish to use regex route, then you could probably use something like:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
new ... Route_Regex(
   "images/products/(\d+)_(\d+)_(\d+).jpg",
   array('controller' =&gt; ...),
   array(1 =&gt; 'id', 2 =&gt; 'width', 3 =&gt; 'height')
);
</code></pre>

<p>And you can of course create your own route implementation.</p>

